thread.title: BRIEF-Starmap Medicine & Technology sees FY 2017 net profit up 115.1 pct to 144.9 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Starmap Medicine & Technology sees FY 2017 net profit up 115.1 pct to 144.9 pct
text:
Jan 30 (Reuters) - Starmap Medicine & Technology Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to increase by 115.1 percent to 144.9 percent, or to be 118.5 million yuan to 134.9 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 55.1 million yuan
* Comments that increased income of health care industry related business and disposition of assets as main reasons for the forecast
